---
title: Caribbean Trout with Coconut Risotto plus Spicy Pepper Relish
description: Tonight’s meal from our chefs is fish-ionary... we’ll wait for your uproarious laughter to subside! For the trout, you’ll make your own special seasoning blend of smoked paprika, ancho chili powder, and garam masala and cook the fillets until flaky. They’ll land on a bed of creamy risotto made luscious with coconut milk, then get topped with a homemade spicy bell pepper relish. This flavorful Caribbean-inspired meal will have you trouting from the rooftops!
